{"word":"μεγαλόφρων","slug":"μεγαλόφρων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεγαλόφρων</b></el> <el>(μεγᾰλό-φρων, ονος, ὁ, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φρήν'><el>φρήν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>high-minded, noble, generous</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in bad sense, <i>arrogant</i>: <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-όνως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}